targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(`date`) AS "time",
  code AS metric,
  CAST(close AS UNSIGNED) AS "close"
FROM daily
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(`date`)
  AND code in ($code)
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(`date`) AS "time",
  code AS metric,
  CAST(moving5 AS DECIMAL(10,1)) AS "moving5",
  CAST(moving20 AS DECIMAL(10,1)) AS "moving20",
  CAST(moving60 AS DECIMAL(10,1)) AS "moving60",
  CAST(moving100 AS DECIMAL(10,1)) AS "moving100"
FROM movingavg
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(`date`)
  AND code in ($code)
ORDER BY time

SELECT
  UNIX_TIMESTAMP(`date`) AS "time",
  code AS metric,
  CAST(trend AS UNSIGNED) AS "trend",
  CAST(continuationDays AS UNSIGNED) AS "continuation",
  (CAST(crossMoving5 AS SIGNED) -2)*5 AS "crossMoving5",
  CASE
    WHEN trendTurn = '2' then NULL
    ELSE CAST(trendTurn AS UNSIGNED)
  END AS trendTurn
FROM trend
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(`date`)
  AND code in ($code)
ORDER BY time
